    <p>If you‚Äôre traveling to Japan in summer, head south to <strong>Okinawa</strong> for beautiful beaches, crystal-clear waters, and tropical weather. Okinawa is ideal for swimming, snorkeling, and diving. The <strong>Kyushu</strong> region also has stunning beaches like <strong>Miyazaki</strong>, which offers a more relaxed and tropical atmosphere, perfect for beach lovers.</p>
    
